first_ability_desc: Notifies all trainers upon entering battle if an opponent has a super-effective super-effective move self-destruct explosion or a one-hit KO move.
second_ability_desc: Causes 1/8 max HP in damage each turn during strong sunlight but heals for 1/8 max HP during rain. Increases damage from fire moves to 1.25X but absorbs water moves healing for 1/4 max HP.
